extends ../_main
block title
	title Minecraft
block content
	h2 <i class="fas fa-swords"></i> Minecraft
	.col-6
		h3 Resource pack
		p This project has been moved to #[a(href='https://github.com/tycrek/tycreks-custom-pack' target='_blank') my GitHub], please go there for any updates.
	.col-6
		h3 Custom Totems
		p Ever wanted your Minecraft skin as a Totem of Undying? Check out my #[a(href="/custom-totem") Custom Totem generator] to get yours! Right now it only works for Minecraft 1.12.2; if there is interest I may add support for more in the future.
	.col-6
		h3 Shaders
		p I've been messing around with shaders lately...... I love them
		blockquote.imgur-embed-pub(lang='en' data-id='a/POLQVw1' data-context='false'): a(href='//imgur.com/a/POLQVw1') Shaders post #1
	.col-6
		h3 Trailer
		p My girlfriend and I made this on our personal survival server using the audio from the original trailer.
		center: video(controls src='/MinecraftTrailerReborn.mp4' style='width: 90%;')
block append scripts
	script(async src='//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js' charset='utf-8')
